    dc:description "FIGURES 47–51. Scarabaspis victoriensis, female. 47, dorsal shield; 48, ventral idiosoma; 49, hypostome; 50, epistome; 51, chelicera. Scale bar = 100 µm for 47, 48; 50 µm for 49, 50, 51." ;
